09:55.226 --> 09:57.393
Did you talk to them?

09:57.395 --> 10:03.400
I did, and they
hadn't seen her since yesterday.

10:03.402 --> 10:11.174
Ok, so not her friends
then where else would she be.

10:11.176 --> 10:18.214
I don't know.
I just want her home.

10:18.216 --> 10:26.089
I just want her home.

10:26.091 --> 10:31.129
Excuse me, I'm going to get
Mrs. Dawn some coffee.

10:51.115 --> 10:52.949
OLIVIA:
Detective Willow?

10:52.951 --> 10:54.818
Yes?

10:54.820 --> 10:57.252
Olivia Peterson. They sent
me down here about a missing

10:57.254 --> 10:59.022
girl case.

10:59.024 --> 11:01.724
Yes, you're the
social worker here.

11:01.726 --> 11:06.729
Um... Yea, we don't get
a lot of cases like this.

11:06.731 --> 11:09.967
No, we do not.
Uh, the state sent me here, uhm,

11:10.999 --> 11:11.901
to talk about some
things with you.

11:11.903 --> 11:16.138
Yeah, well she's a run away so
I don't know what you need.

11:16.140 --> 11:18.141
