the home. Like sexual abuse.

11:22.780 --> 11:25.214
Ok, uhm, right now
she is just gone.

11:25.216 --> 11:28.318
That's all we know, but when we
know more, we'll let you know.

11:28.320 --> 11:31.153
Uh, I really, really, hope I
don't have to call you.

11:31.155 --> 11:32.821
But detective.

11:32.823 --> 11:35.157
If you want to talk
to her, she's right here.

11:35.159 --> 11:39.064
Thank you.

11:40.398 --> 11:45.368
This is Olivia from DHS.

11:45.370 --> 11:48.171
Go ahead.

11:48.173 --> 11:51.907
I know this is a
hard time for you right now.

11:51.909 --> 11:57.946
But can you answer... were there
a lot of men around the house?

11:57.948 --> 12:05.421
Um I date a little.
