14:37.341 --> 14:38.574
Ok.

14:38.576 --> 14:40.343
I want you to stay in the area.

14:40.345 --> 14:41.076
Ok.

14:41.078 --> 14:42.078
Stay positive.

14:42.080 --> 14:44.147
Yea.

14:44.149 --> 14:46.049
If there is anything else...

14:46.051 --> 14:47.083
I know, yeah.

14:47.085 --> 14:48.350
