Nickelodeon, I don't know.

17:33.183 --> 17:35.517
So maybe Sunday night?

17:35.519 --> 17:38.187
Can I join you?

17:38.189 --> 17:41.524
JANE:
Sure.

17:41.526 --> 17:43.191
Jane right?

17:43.193 --> 17:46.295
Yes ma'am.

17:46.297 --> 17:47.763
You know about your friend?

17:47.765 --> 17:51.467
