gone everywhere together.

18:23.468 --> 18:25.571
Do you know where she is?

18:25.903 --> 18:30.275
No.

18:32.576 --> 18:36.578
What are you
thinking about?

18:36.580 --> 18:40.315
I hope she's
somewhere cool. Somewhere fun.

18:40.317 --> 18:43.853
Like on a plane.
Halley loved planes.

18:43.855 --> 18:45.321
Planes?

18:45.323 --> 18:48.924
Yea, she always
wanted to ride one.

18:48.926 --> 18:54.462
We planned it. I would go with
her, we would get on a plane.

18:54.464 --> 18:56.465
Fly away.

18:56.467 --> 19:01.340
Go somewhere awesome.

19:04.308 --> 19:06.275
