19:23.627 --> 19:25.260
That sucks.

19:25.262 --> 19:28.733
Yea.

19:29.968 --> 19:32.802
Let's say Halley
didn't run away.

19:32.804 --> 19:37.273
Maybe somebody took her who
didn't ask her mom's permission.

19:37.275 --> 19:39.976
Do you know
somebody who'd do that?

19:39.978 --> 19:46.315
