bullies. Everybody liked her.

19:46.317 --> 19:49.884
What about her mom?
What do you think of her?

19:49.886 --> 19:53.989
Ms. Dawn?
I've never really met her.

19:53.991 --> 19:57.994
My parents say she is a
little rough around the edges.

19:57.996 --> 19:59.929
How so?

19:59.931 --> 20:02.331
