her mom was hungover.

20:08.373 --> 20:10.273
How long have you known her?

20:10.275 --> 20:12.908
Since the 1st grade.

20:12.910 --> 20:15.044
And she comes over here a lot?

20:15.046 --> 20:19.515
Yea. She said it was
because she gets bored but I

20:19.517 --> 20:23.419
just think she wants to get out
of the house more than anything.

20:23.421 --> 20:25.688
Did she come over
here last night?

20:25.690 --> 20:29.491
No, ma'am.

20:29.493 --> 20:31.526
How did you two meet?

20:31.528 --> 20:34.830
We had the same 1st
grade teacher.

20:34.832 --> 20:37.033
