but two seats were taken.

20:50.048 --> 20:53.849
So we became table neighbors.
Then she moved down

20:53.851 --> 20:58.824
the street, we
became real life neighbors.

21:02.026 --> 21:08.029
I can't even imagine.

21:08.031 --> 21:11.936
That poor girl.

21:15.940 --> 21:18.277
We'll find her.

21:20.077 --> 21:20.776
