22:34.585 --> 22:37.553
Maybe.

22:37.555 --> 22:39.555
You know, maybe some
people just really get off on

22:39.557 --> 22:41.457
that kind of stuff.

22:41.459 --> 22:45.130
Maybe.

22:46.564 --> 22:52.434
I wish you didn't want to leave.

